        <div class="v113-snapshot-grid"><div><strong>2</strong><span>Classes today</span></div><div><strong>6</strong><span>Blockers</span></div><div><strong>$2,845</strong><span>Revenue at risk</span></div><div><strong>4</strong><span>Teacher campaigns</span></div></div>
