      language,
      original:'Keep the original Legal English visible so the learner still practices the real wording.',
      simpleEnglish:'Use Simple English to explain what the page or step means before relying on native-language support.',
      nativeExplanation:`Explain ${page} in ${language} only enough to help the learner get unstuck.`,
      backToLegalEnglish:'Practice the same idea again in Legal English, save it to the lesson folder, or ask a teacher to review it.',
